item.description:
At the home of John Archer (Google John Archer, New York Times).
Donations fund team travel and equipment. Eleanore's Project.org is returning to Peru for the 11th time with wheelchairs, clinicians and techs for children and young adults without mobility. Over 100 people will attend the clinic during the two weeks. This will be my fourth trip. Free free to contact me for additional information.

group.name: Women Supporting Women Through Life's Incredible Journeys
